1030   void node_descriptor_expression() throws ParseException {

8251     for (int i = 0; i < 180; i++) jj_la1[i] = -1;
8252     for (int i = 0; i < jj_2_rtns.length; i++) jj_2_rtns[i] = new JJCalls();
8253   }

8255   /** Reinitialise. */
8256   public void ReInit(JJTreeParserTokenManager tm) {
8257     token_source = tm;
8258     token = new Token();
8259     jj_ntk = -1;
8260     jjtree.reset();
8261     jj_gen = 0;
8262     for (int i = 0; i < 180; i++) jj_la1[i] = -1;
8263     for (int i = 0; i < jj_2_rtns.length; i++) jj_2_rtns[i] = new JJCalls();

8266   private Token jj_consume_token(int kind) throws ParseException {
8267     Token oldToken;
8268     if ((oldToken = token).next != null) token = token.next;
8269     else token = token.next = token_source.getNextToken();
8270     jj_ntk = -1;
8271     if (token.kind == kind) {
8272       jj_gen++;
8273       if (++jj_gc > 100) {
8274         jj_gc = 0;
8275         for (int i = 0; i < jj_2_rtns.length; i++) {
8276           JJCalls c = jj_2_rtns[i];
8277           while (c != null) {
8278             if (c.gen < jj_gen) c.first = null;
8279             c = c.next;
8280           }
8281         }
8282       }
8283       return token;
8284     }
8285     token = oldToken;
8286     jj_kind = kind;
8287     throw generateParseException();
8288   }

8290   static private final class LookaheadSuccess extends java.lang.Error { }
8291   final private LookaheadSuccess jj_ls = new LookaheadSuccess();
8292   private boolean jj_scan_token(int kind) {
8293     if (jj_scanpos == jj_lastpos) {
8294       jj_la--;
8295       if (jj_scanpos.next == null) {
8296         jj_lastpos = jj_scanpos = jj_scanpos.next = token_source.getNextToken();
8297       } else {
8298         jj_lastpos = jj_scanpos = jj_scanpos.next;
8299       }
8300     } else {
8301       jj_scanpos = jj_scanpos.next;
8302     }
8303     if (jj_rescan) {
8304       int i = 0; Token tok = token;
8305       while (tok != null && tok != jj_scanpos) { i++; tok = tok.next; }
8306       if (tok != null) jj_add_error_token(kind, i);
8307     }
8308     if (jj_scanpos.kind != kind) return true;
8309     if (jj_la == 0 && jj_scanpos == jj_lastpos) throw jj_ls;
8310     return false;
8311   }

8316     if (token.next != null) token = token.next;
8317     else token = token.next = token_source.getNextToken();
8318     jj_ntk = -1;
8319     jj_gen++;
8320     return token;
8321   }

8324   final public Token getToken(int index) {
8325     Token t = jj_lookingAhead ? jj_scanpos : token;
8326     for (int i = 0; i < index; i++) {
8327       if (t.next != null) t = t.next;
8328       else t = t.next = token_source.getNextToken();
8329     }
8330     return t;
8331   }

8333   private int jj_ntk() {
8334     if ((jj_nt=token.next) == null)
8335       return (jj_ntk = (token.next=token_source.getNextToken()).kind);
8336     else
8337       return (jj_ntk = jj_nt.kind);
8338   }

8340   private java.util.List<int[]> jj_expentries = new java.util.ArrayList<int[]>();
8341   private int[] jj_expentry;
8342   private int jj_kind = -1;
8343   private int[] jj_lasttokens = new int[100];
8344   private int jj_endpos;
8345 
8346   private void jj_add_error_token(int kind, int pos) {
8347     if (pos >= 100) return;
8348     if (pos == jj_endpos + 1) {
8349       jj_lasttokens[jj_endpos++] = kind;
8350     } else if (jj_endpos != 0) {
8351       jj_expentry = new int[jj_endpos];
8352       for (int i = 0; i < jj_endpos; i++) {
8353         jj_expentry[i] = jj_lasttokens[i];
8354       }
8355       jj_entries_loop: for (java.util.Iterator<?> it = jj_expentries.iterator(); it.hasNext();) {
8356         int[] oldentry = (int[])(it.next());
8357         if (oldentry.length == jj_expentry.length) {
8358           for (int i = 0; i < jj_expentry.length; i++) {
8359             if (oldentry[i] != jj_expentry[i]) {
8360               continue jj_entries_loop;
8361             }
8362           }
8363           jj_expentries.add(jj_expentry);
8364           break jj_entries_loop;
8365         }
8366       }
8367       if (pos != 0) jj_lasttokens[(jj_endpos = pos) - 1] = kind;
8368     }
8369   }

8371   /** Generate ParseException. */
8372   public ParseException generateParseException() {
8373     jj_expentries.clear();
8374     boolean[] la1tokens = new boolean[140];
8375     if (jj_kind >= 0) {
8376       la1tokens[jj_kind] = true;
8377       jj_kind = -1;
8378     }
8379     for (int i = 0; i < 180; i++) {
8380       if (jj_la1[i] == jj_gen) {
8381         for (int j = 0; j < 32; j++) {
8382           if ((jj_la1_0[i] & (1<<j)) != 0) {
8383             la1tokens[j] = true;
8384           }
8385           if ((jj_la1_1[i] & (1<<j)) != 0) {
8386             la1tokens[32+j] = true;
8387           }
8388           if ((jj_la1_2[i] & (1<<j)) != 0) {
8389             la1tokens[64+j] = true;
8390           }
8391           if ((jj_la1_3[i] & (1<<j)) != 0) {
8392             la1tokens[96+j] = true;
8393           }
8394           if ((jj_la1_4[i] & (1<<j)) != 0) {
8395             la1tokens[128+j] = true;
8396           }
8397         }
8398       }
8399     }
8400     for (int i = 0; i < 140; i++) {
8401       if (la1tokens[i]) {
8402         jj_expentry = new int[1];
8403         jj_expentry[0] = i;
8404         jj_expentries.add(jj_expentry);
8405       }
8406     }
8407     jj_endpos = 0;
8408     jj_rescan_token();
8409     jj_add_error_token(0, 0);
8410     int[][] exptokseq = new int[jj_expentries.size()][];
8411     for (int i = 0; i < jj_expentries.size(); i++) {
8412       exptokseq[i] = jj_expentries.get(i);
8413     }
8414     return new ParseException(token, exptokseq, tokenImage);
8415   }

8493   private void jj_save(int index, int xla) {
8494     JJCalls p = jj_2_rtns[index];
8495     while (p.gen > jj_gen) {
8496       if (p.next == null) { p = p.next = new JJCalls(); break; }
8497       p = p.next;
8498     }
8499     p.gen = jj_gen + xla - jj_la; p.first = token; p.arg = xla;
8500   }
